  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f19a602cad3b6213.jpg?v=1782532631\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Recently we got to attend the cutest pop-up hosted by my friend Pamelyn from <a href=\"https://www.shopbasheryandco.com/\">Bashery &amp; Co</a> in Playa Vista as an early Valentine's Day celebration. Of course I'm always looking for any excuse to get dressed up and smooch my favorite little guy!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7b-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0ef6253924568a27.jpg?v=1782532634\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"7c-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/66e47b36382b575d.jpg?v=1782532637\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7d-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/80d3e633e246558a.jpg?v=1782532640\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>There were so many great vendors including <a href=\"http://www.travelingphotobus.com/\">The Traveling Photo Bus</a>,  <a href=\"http://eventivemoments.com/\">Eventive Moments</a>,  <a href=\"http://www.funkyletterboutique.com/\">Funky Letter Boutique</a>, and the coolest group of mamas!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7e-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/078a2c73fb55b183.jpg?v=1782532643\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7f-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0ddf7f187532e59e.jpg?v=1782532646\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7g-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/fcb849648c00f00e.jpg?v=1782532649\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7h-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f05aa30bde667d52.jpg?v=1782532652\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7i-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5bbc8e42b6511dbe.jpg?v=1782532655\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>I wore a dress from Rent The Runway (I'm obsessed right now with their unlimited subscription - more on that soon). Jack's clothes are from <a href=\"http://bit.ly/amykidbox\">Kidbox</a>. To receive 20% off your first order, use the code JACK20 at checkout. Would make an awesome present for Valentine's Day!</p><p>Photos by <a href=\"https://www.ographr.com/\">Ographr</a></p>"
